{"tid":1565210,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［中秋］所有屯門牛同我入黎 ！！！","createTime":"2019-09-13T05:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T14:20:01.000Z","uid":131397,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a5d80746070aba6e95493f146dfeb4184af56eda","tid":1565210,"uid":131397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"913 青雲站 8:00 pm 入青山<br />\n<br />\n中秋佳節。港島太平山，九龍獅子山皆有慶典。一群新界屯門牛捨易取難，夜登青山（香港三尖之一），鍛鍊身心，挑戰自我。<br />\n期待各方加盟或share! <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0299fe5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA</a><br />\n<br />\n時間：8:00p.m.<br />\n第一集合地點<br />\n輕鐡青雲站. <br />\n<br />\n第二集合地點<br />\n青山寺：青雲站行 30分鐘，或<br />\n可以搭的士直達。<br />\n<br />\n階段性目標：半山綠屋企。青山寺起步，新手 30 分鐘都夠。留在此處，一樣可以照亮屯門！進階者可以再上一層樓。<br />\n<br />\n終極目標：山頂！韓凌片石亭，百年古亭。<br />\n<br />\n2030: 最後一批青雲站起步。<br />\n<br />\n2200:  到達山頂。亮燈，照耀屯門。（記得通知地面的牛牛，幫我地影相！😄）<br />\n<br />\n裝備：<br />\n- 身體狀況良好，有行山經驗。要直上500 幾米，夜行更有難度。夜間口訣：黑泥白石光水氹。<br />\n<br />\n- 最少1 公升水。沿途冇補給，溪都冇<br />\n-小量食物<br />\n<br />\n- 長袖風衣，帽。山頂 24 小時好大風及凍。<br />\n-行山仗。<br />\n-蚊怕水<br />\n<br />\n- 急救用品（如有，山上只能自己救自己）<br />\n<br />\n玩樂<br />\n- 強力電筒，鐳射槍 唔少得！<br />\n- 其他無任歡迎。如果你有本事帶上去，再帶返落。<br />\n<br />\n有意見歡迎發表，補充🤗<br />\n群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=0299fe5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YzXDtsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYzXDtsx.jpg&h=49978cef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c005f49bae81ace0920761e2e7ba13366fdc724","tid":1565210,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:14:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EKyy1Mh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEKyy1Mh.png&h=20136a19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tvq2aED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvq2aED.jpg&h=b9168950&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbxHaEE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbxHaEE.jpg&h=b580460a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5brdhjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5brdhjE.jpg&h=561888f2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpDbOrm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmpDbOrm.png&h=68279e52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c5ccb6a09aa347997aa2d5a4593af8d84e92d5c","tid":1565210,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T05:14:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"b7355ef83dddb3d62c6b110679fa8df0f0265800","tid":1565210,"uid":186282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:53:48.000Z","msg":"自己一個毒撚 有無巴絲同行青山"},{"pid":"6c3e6d22d17e5fe338a40cafc34deb03848eb93e","tid":1565210,"uid":295855,